欧洲返美乘客挤爆机场！一片混乱、大部分人没戴口罩...美媒称或有100万美国人将感染病毒。
European Returning Passengers Squeeze Airports! There's chaos, most people don't wear masks... Media says maybe one million Americans will get the virus.
