随着欧洲旅行禁令的生效，美国机场开始加强对欧洲返美乘客的入境检疫。
With the entry into force of the European travel ban, United States airports began to strengthen the immigration quarantine of European passengers returning to the United States.
但由于返美的乘客流量太大，且配套检疫能力不足，3月14日晚美国多个机场陷入了混乱局面。
But many U.S. airports were in disarray on the night of March 14 because of heavy passenger traffic back to the United States and inadequate quarantine capabilities.
美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学发布的实时统计数据显示，截至美国东部时间15日23时（北京时间16日11时），美国新冠肺炎确诊病例累计已达3774例，死亡69例。
According to real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University, the cumulative number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in the United States had reached 3,774 and 69 deaths by 2300 hours (11: 00 Beijing time).
这一数据来自该大学新冠病毒研究项目汇总的美国各州疫情报告。
The data came from a report on state epidemics in the United States compiled by the university's New Crown Virus Research Program.
美国疾病控制和预防中心在周末没有更新数据。
The U. S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention did not update its data over the weekend.
欧洲返美乘客挤爆机场特朗普日前宣布，自本周五（13日）凌晨起暂停30天内从欧洲到美国的所有旅行，14日宣布将禁令扩展至英国和爱尔兰。
Trump has suspended all travel from Europe to the United States for 30 days starting Friday morning and announced the extension of the ban to the United Kingdom and Ireland on Friday.
但美国公民及合法永久居民不受禁令限制，相关航班将被引导至13个指定机场接受入境检疫。
However, United States citizens and legal permanent residents are not subject to the ban and flights will be directed to 13 designated airports for quarantine inspection.
随着欧洲疫情持续恶化，加上对旅行禁令有所担忧，不少滞留欧洲的美国人近日纷纷买票回国。
As the epidemic continues to worsen in Europe, as well as concerns about a travel ban, many Americans in Europe have bought tickets to return home.
纽约肯尼迪机场、芝加哥奥黑尔机场、华盛顿杜勒斯机场、达拉斯沃斯堡机场等多个国际机场周六晚开始人流量激增。
Numerous international airports, including Kennedy Airport in New York, O'Hare Airport in Chicago, Dulles Airport in Washington and Fort Worth Airport in Dallas, began a surge in traffic Saturday night.
但由于边境检疫人力物力不足，大批乘客不得不滞留机场排长队等待入境检疫。
However, due to the lack of human and material resources at the border, a large number of passengers had to wait for quarantine.
有人抱怨等候时间长达数小时，也有人担心原本没生病的自己可能因此感染病毒。
Some complained of waiting for hours, while others feared they might get the virus if they weren't otherwise ill.
现场照片显示，候机厅和过道拥挤不堪，大部分旅客没戴口罩，也没有采取其他防护措施。
Photographs of the scene show congested terminals and aisles, with most passengers not wearing masks and other protective measures.
美国媒体直指，旨在防止疫情扩散至美国的举措，却在生效之际为高传染性的病毒迅速传播创造了完美条件。
The U. S. media have pointed out that measures aimed at preventing the epidemic from spreading to the United States created perfect conditions for the rapid spread of the highly contagious virus at the time of its entry into force.
伊利诺斯州的参议员理查德·德宾就表示，奥黑尔国际机场的入境延误时间长达8个小时，“总统发布欧洲旅行禁令后，行政部门没有做好准备！”面对各方的指责，特朗普3月15日上午回应称：“我们正在机场进行非常精确的医疗检查。
Senator Richard Durbin of Illinois said the airport had been delayed for eight hours and that the administration was "unprepared after the president's European travel ban." Trump responded on the morning of March 15: "We're doing a very accurate medical check-up at the airport.
由此造成不便和延误，敬请谅解。
Please forgive us for any inconvenience and delay.
我们正在尽快行动，但保持警惕和谨慎是非常重要的。
We are moving as quickly as possible, but vigilance and caution are very important.
我们必须确保无误。
We must see to it.
安全第一！”美媒称或有100万美国人将感染新冠病毒11日，在美国国会众议院监督委员会的听证会上，接受问询的专家表示，美国疫情的拐点还远没有到来。
One million Americans could be infected with the New Crown Virus, media reported on Tuesday at a hearing before the House Oversight Committee that the turning point for the U.S. epidemic is far from over.
据《时代周刊》报道，为美国疾控中心提供传播模型的实验室提供的数据显示，美国已错过遏制新冠病毒最佳时期，预计全国感染人数将在4月底达到峰值，可能有高达100万人的美国人被感染。
According to Time magazine, data from laboratories providing models for the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention in the United States show that the United States has missed its peak in containment of the new crown virus, with national infections expected to peak by the end of April, with as many as one million Americans likely to be infected.
Play中国以外新冠肺炎确诊病例超过8.6万例美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学发布的实时统计数据显示，截至北京时间3月16日8时33分，全球新冠肺炎累计确诊病例已超过16.7万例，其中中国以外地区累计确诊病例超过8.6万例。
According to real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University in the United States, more than 167,000 cases of pneumonia have been confirmed worldwide, including more than 86,000 cases outside China, according to real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University in the US.
意大利单日新增确诊3590例累计确诊24747例当地时间15日18时，意大利现存新冠肺炎确诊病例20603例，其中重症1672例；累计治愈出院2335例；新增死亡368例，累计死亡1809例。
The total number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Italy was 20,603, of which 1,672 were severe. The total number of cases cured was 2,335, 368 new deaths and 1,809 cumulative deaths.
截至目前，意大利累计确诊24747例，较前一天增加3590例。
So far, 24,747 cases have been diagnosed in Italy, 3590 more than the previous day.
伊朗国家动员计划已完成1000万人的疫情排查工作据伊朗塔斯尼姆通讯社15日消息，目前伊朗国家动员计划已经完成1000万人的疫情排查工作。
Iran's national mobilization plan has been cleared of 10 million people, Iran's national mobilization plan has been completed 10 million people, according to Iran's Tasmanian news agency 15, said.
其中21万人出现头痛、发热等症状，其中3万人由于症状严重被送往医疗中心、1200人被转至医院、900人住院治疗。
Of these, 210,000 had headaches, fever and other symptoms, of which 30,000 were taken to medical centres, 1,200 to hospitals and 900 to hospitals due to severe symptoms.
此外，根据伊朗卫生部最新指令，伊朗红新月会将前往各城市的进出口通道监测来往人员。
In addition, according to the latest directive of the Iranian Ministry of Health, the Iranian Red Crescent will travel to and from the cities to monitor traffic.
此外，火车站、大巴站以及机场等的疫情监测工作也由该组织负责。
In addition, the organization is responsible for monitoring outbreaks at railway stations, bus stations and airports.
日本累计确诊818例 累计死亡24例据日本放送协会消息，根据日本各地的地方自治团体和厚生劳动省通报的数据，截至当地时间15日22时30分，日本国内累计确诊804人，加上包机归国的确诊病例14例，累计确诊818例。
According to the Japan Broadcasting Association, 818 cases of cumulative deaths have been confirmed in Japan. According to data reported by local self-government organizations and the Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare throughout Japan, 804 people had been diagnosed in Japan as of 22: 30 local time, plus 14 confirmed cases returned home by chartered flights, making a cumulative total of 818 confirmed cases.
目前，日本国内累计死亡人数24例。
At present, the cumulative death toll in Japan is 24.
法国单日新增确诊923例 累计确诊5423例根据法国公共健康局官方网站的最新通报，截至当地时间15日15时，法国累计确诊5423例，较前一日新增923例。
A total of 5,423 new cases were diagnosed in France in a single day. By 1500 hours local time, a total of 5,423 cases had been diagnosed, an increase of 923 over the previous day, according to the official website of the French Public Health Office.
英国单日新增确诊232例 累计确诊1372例600多名专家学者发公开信呼吁政府改变消极措施据英国卫生与社会保障部统计，从当地时间14日9时至15日9时，英国新增确诊232例，累计确诊1372例；新增死亡14例，累计死亡35例。
Britain confirmed 232 new cases in one day More than 1,600 experts and scholars issued an open letter calling on the government to change negative measures From 9: 00 a.m. to 9: 00 a.m. local time, 232 new cases were confirmed in the UK, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 1,372, with 14 new deaths and 35 cumulative deaths.
另据英国媒体报道，英国监狱官员协会秘书长吉蓝表示，目前英国监狱系统已经有113名职员和75名服刑犯因出现疑似新冠病毒症状正在进行隔离，尚未有人确诊。
A total of 113 staff and 75 prisoners serving sentences are being quarantined for suspected new crown virus symptoms and no one has yet been identified, British media reported.
目前，英国还没有因疫情而提前释放关押犯人的计划，但是不排除这种可能。
Britain has no plans to release prisoners early because of the outbreak, but that is not to be ruled out.
面对日益严峻的疫情形势，来自英国多所大学和科研机构的600多名专家学者发布公开信，要求英国政府增强防疫手段，以免在未来短时间内面对灾难后果。
More than 600 experts and scholars from British universities and research institutes have issued an open letter asking the British government to step up preventive measures so as to avoid the consequences of the disaster in the near future.
德国单日新增确诊过千例将关闭与5国间边境截至当地时间15日15时，德国疾控机构罗伯特·科赫研究所发布的数据显示，德国累计确诊4838例，较上一日增长了1043例，累计死亡12例。
More than 1,000 cases to be confirmed in Germany By 1500 local time, data released by the German CDC's Robert Koch Institute showed a cumulative total of 4,838 confirmed cases in Germany, an increase of 1,043 from the previous day and 12 cumulative deaths.
德国政府决定，关闭对法国、瑞士和奥地利、丹麦和卢森堡的边境。
The German government decided to close its borders with France, Switzerland and Austria, Denmark and Luxembourg.
北欧四国累计确诊超2600例截至15日20时，挪威累计确诊1234例，累计死亡3例。
At 20: 00 on the 15th, the total number of confirmed cases in Norway was 1234, with a total of 3 deaths.
截至15日14时，芬兰单日新增确诊20例，累计确诊244例。
As of 14: 00 on the 15th, 20 new cases were diagnosed in Finland in a single day, and 244 cases were diagnosed.
截至15日14时，瑞典累计确诊992例，累计死亡2例。
As of 1400 hours on the 15th, a cumulative total of 992 cases and 2 cumulative deaths had been diagnosed in Sweden.
截至15日17时，冰岛单日新增确诊43例，累计确诊177例。
As of 17: 00 on the 15th, Iceland confirmed 43 new cases a day, a cumulative total of 177 cases.
